{"tid":524711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寶馬男撞車逃走 被撞五人跑足500米截司機","createTime":"2018-01-10T00:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T03:09:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ca61df74f69774042ed65539e55fe154a5468cfe","tid":524711,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:40:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1108859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1108859%2F&d=wbybNbZG5TiC%2FlbXGPiTWMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d4b1b8f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1108859%2F&h=66d26ac4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1108859/</a><br />\n<br />\n一輛載有一名女乘客的寶馬凌晨兩時許，沿青衣青葵公路往九龍方向行駛，過了長青隧道一個彎位，失控撞向路中石壆及「打白鴿轉」，並與一輛客貨車相撞，意外後姓陳35歲男司機寶馬司機下車，越過石壆到對面線，往青衣南橋方向逃走。<br />\n<br />\n被撞客貨車姓李36歲司機及四名男乘客立即追趕，窮追500米將司機截獲，更稱眾人「跑馬拉松，咁都夠膽走」。警方接報到場，發現寶馬沒有行車證，調查證實有購買行車證，不過沒有展示。司機沒有醉駕藥駕，但沒有展示行車證，被警方票控。男司機聲稱頸痛不適，需送院治理。"},{"pid":"5d595759e4f5a3e9331994751f9b22e6d78ca7d6","tid":524711,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:40:28.000Z","msg":"據了解，已婚女乘客與涉事男司機屬朋友，男司機向友人借用寶馬，當時送女乘客返荃灣象山邨住所途中。"},{"pid":"9d1d28fb509a792ce43218663c9b8470c9806071","tid":524711,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d595759e4f5a3e9331994751f9b22e6d78ca7d6","tid":524711,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:40:28.000Z","msg":"據了解，已婚女乘客與涉事男司機屬朋友，男司機向友人借用寶馬，當時送女乘客返荃灣象山邨住所途中。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b81b8b919731cfc19cf41cdb0920d9f3e6c08b","tid":524711,"uid":71342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d595759e4f5a3e9331994751f9b22e6d78ca7d6","tid":524711,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:40:28.000